things like that,

00:47:24.942 --> 00:47:27.067
would be enough to solve
the wealth inequality gap.

00:47:27.067 --> 00:47:29.424
Have you guys done any
quantitative modeling

00:47:29.424 --> 00:47:33.408
to see if, let's say what would
happen if 100% of the top 5,000

00:47:33.408 --> 00:47:35.649
companies adopted
this, like what

00:47:35.649 --> 00:47:37.392
would be the impact
on wealth inequality?

00:47:37.392 --> 00:47:40.271
