You are correct that if you
look at the stock market

00:53:17.390 --> 00:53:20.210
the NASDAQ and NYSE
I think probably

00:53:20.210 --> 00:53:22.210
about 17 trillion
dollars today--

00:53:22.210 --> 00:53:24.930
private equity is already
several trillion dollars,

00:53:24.930 --> 00:53:26.550
so you can't deal
with this issue

00:53:26.550 --> 00:53:28.480
unless you have approach
to private equity.

00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:32.590
You're absolutely
on the button there.

